data.description: Welcome to your spacious oasis of serenity! Nestled on just under 3 acres, this home offers ample room for the entire family with four bedrooms & two generously sized living rooms for gathering. At this home, you can spend your mornings on the large front porch and spend your evenings relaxing on the screened-in back porch. The 30x40 detached metal shop is a dream come true - whether you're a car aficionado, a DIY enthusiast, or simply need a space for your hobbies, this shop offers the perfect solution! If you're in need of more storage space, the backyard has two outbuildings ready to house your tools, equipment, or hobby supplies. This home is convenient to town, yet with its long driveway and being surrounded by greenery, it feels quiet and remote - it's the perfect blend of space, comfort, and privacy.
